{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_li_si","speaker_name":"李斯","listener":null,"text":"肖老病倒哩！","tone":"焦急","chapter":120,"line_start":4,"line_end":6},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yue_tan","speaker_name":"肖月潭","listener":null,"text":"我不行哩！","tone":"苦笑","chapter":120,"line_start":12,"line_end":13},{"speaker":"char_ji_yan_ran","speaker_name":"纪嫣然","listener":"char_xiao_yue_tan","text":"肖先生休息两天就会没事的了。","tone":"温柔","chapter":120,"line_start":16,"line_end":17},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yue_tan","speaker_name":"肖月潭","listener":"char_ji_yan_ran","text":"肖某精通医道，病况如何自家晓得，我想和少龙单独说几句话。","tone":"淡然","chapter":120,"line_start":18,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yue_tan","speaker_name":"肖月潭","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"真不好意思，累得廷芳都哭了，但不如此，又怕骗不过小武和小恬。","tone":"无奈","chapter":120,"line_start":26,"line_end":28},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_xiao_yue_tan","text":"肖兄准备不回咸阳了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":120,"line_start":30,"line_end":31},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yue_tan","speaker_name":"肖月潭","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"我再也不能忍受以笑脸迎对那奸贼，他今趟是全心把我除去，好削弱图爷的势力，以他吕族的人代之。但又不敢明目张胆这么做，怕人说他不念旧情。","tone":"无奈","chapter":120,"line_start":32,"line_end":35},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yue_tan","speaker_name":"肖月潭","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"我诈死的事，除李斯、滕翼和少龙你外，只可让图爷一人知道。少龙请把信函亲自交给图爷，他看过便会明白，同时请他为我遣散家中的妾婢仆人，幸好我无儿无女，否则想走也很难办到。","tone":"认真","chapter":120,"line_start":36,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_xiao_yue_tan","text":"肖兄准备到哪里去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":120,"line_start":44,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yue_tan","speaker_name":"肖月潭","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"天下这么大，何处不能容身？我肖月潭还有些可出卖的小玩意，想要求一宿两餐，应该没有问题，总好过与虎同室。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":120,"line_start":48,"line_end":50},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yue_tan","speaker_name":"肖月潭","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"当我有落脚之处，自会使人告知少龙。记着回去后，千万要装作若无其事。阳泉君的野心虽给吕不韦夸大，但本身亦非善男信女，藉机除掉他应是好事，至于会牵连多少人，就非我们能控制了。","tone":"认真","chapter":120,"line_start":54,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yue_tan","speaker_name":"肖月潭","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"吕族的人里，若诸萌在横龙岭一役果然丧命，那吕族将暂时没有可成气候的人，只要他一天仍倚重图爷，图爷应可照拂你们。记得回咸阳后立即引退，没有必要，千万不要见姬后和政太子，此乃保命之道。","tone":"认真","chapter":120,"line_start":60,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yue_tan","speaker_name":"肖月潭","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"今夜由你们掩护我秘密溜掉，就把整个营帐烧掉，说是我的遗命，少龙！小心点了，李斯在吕不韦眼中乃微不足道的小人物，回去亦不会有事。想不到此人才智学养均如此高明，异日将可成为你有力臂助。","tone":"认真","chapter":120,"line_start":68,"line_end":74}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiang_shao_long","name":"项少龙","alias":[],"identity":"来自二十一世纪的穿越者","faction":"faction_qin_guo","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"来自二十一世纪的穿越者，秦王信任的将领，痛失娇妻后意欲退隐","personality":{"traits":["重情重义","隐忍坚毅","智勇双全","恩怨分明","心怀天下"],"speech_style":"沉稳内敛，少言但每句有分量","temperament":"外冷内热"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_yue_tan","type":"挚友","intensity":75,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"共患难"},{"target":"char_zhao_qian","type":"恋人","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"痛失爱妻"},{"target":"char_wu_ting_fang","type":"恋人","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"相伴"},{"target":"char_ji_yan_ran","type":"恋人","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"相伴"},{"target":"char_lv_bu_wei","type":"宿敌","intensity":85,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"隐忍待发"},{"target":"char_xiao_pan","type":"师徒","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"秘密守护"},{"target":"char_zhuang_xiang_wang","type":"主仆","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"信任但心怀愧疚"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[120],"source_refs":[{"chapter":120,"line_start":2,"line_end":2,"text":"先不要说项少龙现在对出使各国的事意冷心灰"},{"chapter":120,"line_start":24,"line_end":24,"text":"项少龙目瞪口呆时，才醒悟到他是以易容术在装重病"}]},{"id":"char_xiao_yue_tan","name":"肖月潭","alias":["肖老"],"identity":"图先手下谋士，精通医道和易容术","faction":"faction_qin_guo","role":"companion","archetype":"scholar","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"足智多谋的谋士，精通医道和易容术，因吕不韦迫害而诈死隐退","personality":{"trait